after the surrender of geronimo in 1886 , the apache threat was essentially extinguished , but the army continued to operate fort huachuca because of its strategic border position .

cowboys & indians : ( jon of the clue crew reports from fort huachuca , az. )   fort huachuca was built in 1877 as part of the wars with this tribe ; that purpose was ended with geronimo 's capture in 1886

